summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Land Use and Zoning; amending Plat 36E, Page 103 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone Block 47 of John H. Nagle's Addition to the City of Seattle, located at 100 to 122 Harvard Avenue East from Midrise (MR) to Midrise/Residential-Commercial (MR/RC) Zone. (Petition of Larry Heath, C.F. 295541.)
